import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
from scipy.stats import pearsonr

# 假设你已有两个数组：x, y
x = data["NolEntranceGrade"]
y = data["AveGradeTerm01"]

# 计算皮尔逊相关系数和 p 值
r, p_value = pearsonr(x, y)

# 创建散点图 + 回归线
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 5))
sns.regplot(x=x, y=y, scatter_kws={'alpha': 0.6, 'edgecolor': 'k'}, line_kws={'color': 'red'})

# 标题中显示 Pearson r 和 P 值
plt.title(f"Correlation: r = {r:.2f}, p = {p_value:.4f}", fontsize=14)
plt.xlabel("X")
plt.ylabel("Y")
plt.grid(True, linestyle=":")
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

x = data["NolEntranceGrade"]
y_vars = ["AveGradeTerm01", "AveGradeTerm02", "FailedCsTerm01"]
y_vars_name = ["Term01-AveGrade", "Term02-AveGrade", "Term01-Fail"]
titles = ["Term 01", "Term 02", "Fail Count"]
y_limla = [[45, 95], [45, 95], [-0.5, 10.5]]
y_limlab = [[45, 95], [45, 95], [0, 10]]
zeta = [5,5,1]

fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 3, figsize=(18, 5), facecolor='white')

for i, y_var in enumerate(y_vars):
    y = data[y_var]
    r, p = pearsonr(x, y)

    sns.regplot(x=x, y=y, ax=axes[i], color = "#105186",
                scatter_kws={'alpha': 0.6, 'edgecolor': 'face'},
                line_kws={'color': '#BE3428', 'linewidth':5})

    axes[i].set_title(f"r={r:.2f}, p={p:.4f}", fontsize=16)
    axes[i].set_xlabel("EntranceScore", fontsize = 16)
    axes[i].set_ylabel(y_vars_name[i], fontsize=16)
    axes[i].set_xlim([-0.02, 1.02])
    axes[i].set_xticks(np.arange(0,  1.02, 0.1))
    axes[i].set_ylim(y_limla[i])
    axes[i].set_yticks(np.arange(y_limlab[i][0],  y_limlab[i][1]+1, zeta[i]))
    axes[i].grid(True, linestyle=":", linewidth=1.5)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
In [5]:
x = data["NolEntranceGrade"]
y_vars = ["AveGradeTerm01", "AveGradeTerm02", "FailedCsTerm01"]
y_vars_name = ["Term01-AveGrade", "Term02-AveGrade", "Term01-Fail"]
y_limla = [[45, 95], [45, 95], [-0.5, 10.5]]
y_limlab = [[45, 95], [45, 95], [0, 10]]
zeta = [5, 5, 1]
locll = ["lower left", "lower left", "upper right"]

fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 3, figsize=(18, 5), facecolor='white')

for i, y_var in enumerate(y_vars):
    y = data[y_var]
    r, p = pearsonr(x, y)

    # 绘制回归线 + 散点
    sns.regplot(x=x, y=y, ax=axes[i], color="#105186",
                scatter_kws={'alpha': 0.3, 'edgecolor': 'face', 's': 150},  # 设置散点大小 s
                line_kws={'color': '#BE3428', 'linewidth': 6,
                          'label': f"r={r:.2f}, p={p:.4f}"}, ci=95)  # 把 r, p 当作图例

    # 设置图形属性
    axes[i].set_xlabel("Entrance Score", fontsize=24)
    axes[i].set_ylabel(y_vars_name[i], fontsize=24)
    axes[i].set_xlim([-0.02, 1.02])
    axes[i].set_xticks(np.arange(0, 1.02, 0.1))
    axes[i].set_ylim(y_limla[i])
    axes[i].set_yticks(np.arange(y_limlab[i][0], y_limlab[i][1] + 1, zeta[i]))

    # 样式美化
    axes[i].grid(True, linestyle=":", linewidth=1.5)
    axes[i].legend(loc=locll[i], fontsize=24)  # 图例位置调整

plt.tight_layout()
# plt.savefig("G://University//GradePrediction//processwork//figure//figure 05 b.png", dpi=600, bbox_inches='tight', transparent=False)
plt.show()
